{"base_path":null,"components":null,"consumes":"[\"application/json;charset=UTF-8\"]","definitions":{"CreateDataImageRequest":{"properties":{"volume_id":{"description":"数据卷ID。","example":"8a12fc664fb4daa3014fb4e581380005","type":"string"}},"required":["volume_id"]},"MakeImage200":{"properties":{"job_id":{"description":"任务ID。","example":"8a12fc664fb4daa3014fb4e581380005","type":"string"}}},"MakeImageReq":{"properties":{"architecture":{"description":"镜像CPU架构类型,取值为x86_64或者aarch64。","example":"x86_64","type":"string"},"data_images":{"description":"数据卷ID列表,当前列表中只支持一个数据卷ID。","items":{"$ref":"#/definitions/CreateDataImageRequest"},"type":"array"},"description":{"description":"镜像描述信息。支持字母、数字、中文等,不支持回车、<、 >,长度不能超过1024个字符。默认为空。","example":"Creating an ImageFunction","maxLength":1024,"pattern":"[^<>\r\n]+","type":"string"},"domain":{"description":"共享服务器的用户所属的域。","example":"******","type":"string"},"encrypt_cipher":{"description":"若FusionSphere OpenStack安装部署界面的“运维>证书管理>Swift密钥管理 > Swift对象加密”为打开的状态且对接的存储后端是swift时可以选择对应的加密算法(通用场景对称算法为AES, SM系列商密场景对称算法为SM4)。AES(Advanced Encryption Standard)即高级加密标准,它是一个迭代的、对称密钥分组的密码,可以使用256位密钥,并且用128位分组加密。\nSM4是一种32轮的迭代非平衡Feistel结构的分组加密算法,其密钥长度和分组长度均为128。","enum":["AES","SM4"],"type":"string"},"hw_firmware_type":{"description":"镜像启动模式,取值为bios或者uefi。","example":"bios","type":"string"},"image_url":{"description":"镜像存储后端是OBS:OBS桶中外部镜像文件地址。在使用OBS桶的外部镜像文件制作镜像时生效且为必选字段。格式为<OBS桶名>:<OBS镜像文件名称>(外部文件制作镜像时必选)。镜像存储后端是Swift:当trans_mode取值是shared时,image_url表示共享文件的路径地址。格式为 \\\\共享服务器IP\\共享路径\\共享文件(外部文件制作镜像时必选)。","example":"ims-image:centos70.qcow2","type":"string"},"instance_id":{"description":"需要转换的云服务器ID。使用instance_id字段,从云服务器制作私有镜像时,该字段填写云服务器ID(云服务器制作镜像时必选)。","example":"877a2cda-ba63-4e1e-b95f-e67e48b6129a","type":"string"},"is_config":{"description":"是否自动配置。取值为true或false。如果需要后台自动配置,取值为true,否则为false。","example":true,"type":"boolean"},"is_config_init":{"description":"是否完成了初始化配置。取值为true或false。如果用户确定完成了初始化配置,则可以设置为true,否则设置为false。默认为false。","example":true,"type":"boolean"},"is_supported_encrypt":{"description":"是否开启传输加密,取值:support(开启),notSupport(不开启)。加密传输只支持windows8或windows server2012及以上的操作系统。","example":"support,notSupport","type":"string"},"min_disk":{"description":"最小系统盘大小。在使用外部镜像文件制作镜像时生效且为必选字段。","example":40,"type":"integer"},"name":{"description":"镜像名称(必选)。","example":"ims_test","type":"string"},"os_version":{"description":"操作系统版本。使用上传至OBS桶中或者共享目录的外部系统盘镜像文件制作镜像时生效,具体取值,请参见《华为云Stack 8.3.0 资源发放指南》“计算服务 > 镜像服务(IMS)> 常见问题 >  公共镜像参数说明”章节。","example":"CentOS 7.0 64bit","type":"string"},"password":{"description":"共享服务器的用户密码。","example":"******","type":"string"},"trans_mode":{"description":"镜像存储后端是Swift时申请私有镜像的方式,取值:shared(共享方式)。","example":"shared","type":"string"},"user_name":{"description":"共享服务器的用户名。","example":"******","type":"string"}},"required":["name"],"type":"object"}},"description":null,"group_id":"222a050bd51b4fdba0ebd8e5baa98679","host":"hcs.cn-north-4.myhuaweicloud.com","id":"a12a590cc8e24bdb8c9ac1d9921b8be4","info_version":"v1","method":"post","name":"CreateImage","parameters":{},"paths":{"/v2/cloudimages/action":{"post":{"description":"使用云服务器、上传至OBS桶中或者共享目录的外部镜像文件制作私有的系统盘镜像,或者使用云硬盘制作私有的数据盘镜像。作为异步接口,调用成功,只是说明后台收到了制作请求,镜像是否制作成功需要通过查询Job状态接口查询该任务的执行状态,具体请参考本文档“查询Job状态”章节。","operationId":"CreateImage","parameters":[{"default":"application/json","description":"发送的实体的MIME类型。推荐用户默认使用application/json,如果API是对象、镜像上传等接口,媒体类型可按照流类型的不同进行确定。","enum":["application/json"],"in":"header","name":"Content-Type","required":true,"type":"string"},{"description":"请求body长度,单位为Byte。","in":"header","name":"Content-Length","required":false,"type":"string"},{"description":"用户Token。","in":"header","name":"X-Auth-Token","pattern":"[\\\\w\\\\-\\\\+=]*","required":true,"type":"string"},{"description":"This is a auto create Body Object","in":"body","name":"MakeImageReq","required":true,"schema":{"$ref":"#/definitions/MakeImageReq"}}],"produces":["application/json"],"responses":{"200":{"description":"OK  请求正常。","schema":{"$ref":"#/definitions/Make